    <item>
      <title>投票后，破坏者雅各布·祖马掌握着南非的命运</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/south-africa-elections-jacob-zuma-has-south-africa-s-fate-in-his-hands</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雅各布·祖马在被执政党非洲人国民大会赶下台之前，曾领导南非近九年，但饱受丑闻困扰。如今，他可能在南非的政治前途中扮演重要角色。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/south-africa-elections-jacob-zuma-has-south-africa-s-fate-in-his-hands</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 10:27:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据报道，俄亥俄州枪击事件造成一人死亡，数十人受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-02/overnight-shooting-in-ohio-street-kills-1-man-and-wounds-26-other-people-news-reports-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄亥俄州阿克伦（美联社）——警方称，俄亥俄州一条街道上凌晨发生枪击事件，造成一人死亡，24 人受伤，其中一些伤势严重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-02/overnight-shooting-in-ohio-street-kills-1-man-and-wounds-26-other-people-news-reports-say</guid>
